Properties.Caption: Просмотр паспортов по 0409
Properties.Tag: Select [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [DOC].[DU_R] As [Дата утверждения распорядителя], [REP_DESC].[CODE8] As [Код показателя 0409], Max([REP_DESC].[NAME]) As [Наименование показателя 0409], [Apps_ObjectProperties].[PropertyValue] As [Значение показателя 0409], Sum([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[SUMM]) As [Год Текущий Значение], Sum([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[SUMM_1]) As [Год 1 Значение], Sum([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[SUMM_2]) As [Год 2 Значение], Sum([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[SUMM_3]) As [Год 3 Значение] From (((([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [REP_DESC] With (NoLock) On ([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[REP_DESCID]=[REP_DESC].[REP_DESCID])) Inner Join [Apps_ObjectProperties] With (NoLock) On ([PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[Apps_ObjectsID]=[Apps_ObjectProperties].[Apps_ObjectsID] And Nz(210,[PRB_0409_REP_SUMM].[Apps_ObjectsID])=[Apps_ObjectProperties].[Apps_PropertyNamesID])) Where |0 Group by [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DU_R], [REP_DESC].[CODE8], [Apps_ObjectProperties].[PropertyValue] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр паспортов по 0409
